  change over time."""@en ;
  curric:whyThisWhyNow """Pupils can build on their understanding of global inequalities and on
  their study of Indonesia to consider the global pattern of urbanisation. Pupils can use their
  knowledge gained in the subsequent unit on Jakarta.""" ;
